name: blue woman with sad feelings
description: I draw with my own feelings with the color I choose, "like what you like" but I can only feel fear, it doesn't go according to expectations even I continue to struggle with anxiety feelings of regret become so sad in tears. every time i walk, it hurts so much "Keep doing what you love" but it's not for fun, if I can do it I can only be a blank canvas in the journey of my life.
